revision.text: ==Alangan== ===Etymology=== From {{inh|alj|poz-pro|*ʀabiqi||late afternoon, evening, evening meal, yesterday}}, from {{inh|alj|map-pro|*ʀabiqi||late afternoon, evening, evening meal}}. ===Noun=== {{head|alj|noun|head=yabì}} # [[night]]; [[evening]] ---- ==Mansaka== ===Etymology=== Ultimately from {{der|msk|pt|chave}}. ===Noun=== {{head|msk|noun}} # [[key]] ---- ==Papiamentu== [[File:Llave bronce.jpg|150px|right|thumb]] ===Etymology=== From {{der|pap|pt|chave}} and {{bor|pap|es|llave}} and {{der|pap|kea|tchabi}}. ===Noun=== {{head|pap|noun}} # [[key]] ---- ==Sambali== ===Etymology=== From {{inh|xsb|poz-pro|*ʀabiqi||late afternoon, evening, evening meal, yesterday}}, from {{inh|xsb|map-pro|*ʀabiqi||late afternoon, evening, evening meal}}. ===Noun=== {{head|xsb|noun|head=yabí}} # [[evening]]; [[night]]
